{"tid":720251,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(真心求教) 到底facebook上面啲「巴打絲打谷」係乜撚野黎 同連登舊登有咩關係??","createTime":"2018-06-27T19:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T08:55:12.000Z","uid":182994,"like":7,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9d1b418772cf208021cd970d70f61d954a0ce986","tid":720251,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T19:08:05.000Z","msg":"話說大概上兩個星期，屋企人同啲好日都唔見既遠房親戚飲茶。<br />\n有對我稱呼佢地做表叔表嬸既中年夫婦(其實都疏到唔知係咪咁叫，不過細個屋企人話咁叫就咁叫)，佢地係啲一把年紀口沒遮攔又要扮潮扮醒果啲中坑，我都唔知點形容，大概係以下兩位大家討論過既youtuber咁既格。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/021826_26c9cb444c63587741a6b323ac1aa672.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F021826_26c9cb444c63587741a6b323ac1aa672.png&h=740e4e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路飲其實我都冇點出聲，不過飲飲下佢地係度開始講咩「巴打絲打谷」，講下佢地啲「谷友」分享左咩「潮野」。成枱人都唔知佢up乜，佢地就開始話其他人out喇乜乜柒柒，然後又話乜我咁後生都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n本身聽到佢地講巴打絲打以為佢地講連登或者舊登啦，搞左一大輪先知係facebook group。之後就引起左我既興趣，話曬上左咁多年舊登之後又轉左黎連登，都冇聽過有巴絲開左facebook group。<br />\n<br />\n於是我就係facebook search然後求其入左一個類似既group，之後係度睇啲人啲post，笑撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大部分都係類似成長左既mk妹mk仔咁既人，成9日都會post果啲乜7語錄金句或者類似既野<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/023738_614a1c4a826221c7a6fc1942c4d1dac3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F023738_614a1c4a826221c7a6fc1942c4d1dac3.png&h=784c379b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/023828_3734c398d3021f11c19973ee445eda9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F023828_3734c398d3021f11c19973ee445eda9c.png&h=5e439848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好好笑既post，有啲係正常人唔suppose想畀人知真身既post，當事人都係就咁post出黎，勁似奇呢真人版既連登同舊登<br />\n<br />\n好似有條友係個group度問有咩避孕丸有咩副作用，問問下變左問女網友中出係咪爽啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，個女網友仲要話自己唔中意用套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好想知佢地啲親戚朋友見到會點<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/025214_db068e7cf1d1a96de0b184638d400657.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F025214_db068e7cf1d1a96de0b184638d400657.png&h=6559d03b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/025215_71db562268a3803b1f87666a0054c939.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F025215_71db562268a3803b1f87666a0054c939.png&h=c4d4a1dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/025215_75045c3f321ff3a929c688adbdcc038e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F025215_75045c3f321ff3a929c688adbdcc038e.png&h=8a49b3e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又會有啲人post啲正常人唔會想畀外人既家事出黎問意見，同其他千奇百趣既post<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/025731_e7c2e38e819da2c7db8b3722dafb9c5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F025731_e7c2e38e819da2c7db8b3722dafb9c5e.png&h=96650114&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/025732_0df5fe4398a0203345a9a97a2d064bbc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F025732_0df5fe4398a0203345a9a97a2d064bbc.png&h=db7a38ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/025733_0df5fe4398a0203345a9a97a2d064bbc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F025733_0df5fe4398a0203345a9a97a2d064bbc.png&h=336da81b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個group又有兩個admin，出親post都大把人留言，周不時又有好多人討論，個個group都有幾萬人，十足KOL咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/025921_f5904a9dba1153b778fcb64d4c98901b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F025921_f5904a9dba1153b778fcb64d4c98901b.png&h=0325a271&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/025922_6b5330c1e69de1b629f3d019e05143ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F025922_6b5330c1e69de1b629f3d019e05143ee.png&h=7512a229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明佢地啲又好似平平無其咁，冇咩值得人討論既地方，到底係何方神聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲group又係咩來頭，同兩登有冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解我用左咁多年facebook都冇留意過有呢啲野，真心想知同真心求教"},{"pid":"65c20f1ef07bc7d9ee188e1ddc3898881a137840","tid":720251,"uid":159071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T19:12:28.000Z","msg":"個group由9add人開始做起，跟住開始有人出post，慢慢變到好多mk仔女食花生嘅集中地。"},{"pid":"1368aa4fb0cbb9576562701df66c8f6e32d7b970","tid":720251,"uid":38915,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T19:13:52.000Z","msg":"我report過fb無受理"},{"pid":"6668a2e519d1c1f461519d489c9fbf77d9fb50db","tid":720251,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"65c20f1ef07bc7d9ee188e1ddc3898881a137840","tid":720251,"uid":159071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T19:12:28.000Z","msg":"個group由9add人開始做起，跟住開始有人出post，慢慢變到好多mk仔女食花生嘅集中地。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T19:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/032145_21a14830159a50542d90a7bcaf4c7227.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F032145_21a14830159a50542d90a7bcaf4c7227.png&h=b7d410